{
  "stem": "16.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I, I saw dead people next to me left and right, all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that is in, in, in my nightmares many times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Faceless people-- because I didn't know any of them in person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But how they died, how nobody cared is just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three days before we actually got liberated, the Swiss Red Cross was allowed to stop.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every single prisoner got a small little package.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- it may have been already in May, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I got liberated May the 8th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got-- we got a little package of, like, a K-ration.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told, do not eat all of it at one time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just ration yourself, or else you get dysentery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, some people didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were in-- inside the train that was traveling for eight days and eight nights, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one morning, everything is at a standstill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The train is standing there for hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's just started to get daylight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody looks out the window and says, hey, there's a strange uniform out there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Must be a Polish uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says-- another one, no, that looks like a Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, pick me up!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Pick me up!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the window was very high, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so somebody picked me up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, this is an American soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's an Eisenhower-- and we saw one Eisenhower jacket with a Tommy gun-- one soldier, nobody else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And minutes later, all the doors opened up-- and, like, 2,000 prisoners out of those wagons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Germans started to tear off their ranks and threw down their guns-- and holding their hands high in the air.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
